<tr>
<td valign="top" class="contentText">
Analysis offers users and vendors in Italy an in-depth view of the external services providers markets and issues. Coverage includes assistance in deciding when, why and what areas to outsource. 
How should European user organisations who are increasingly using external IT services suppliers, replace or supplement their existing IT methods. Is your organisation considering such a move? If so, what are the risks and benefits? 
<p />

The External Services Providers Italy (ESPI) research team offers users and vendors in Italy an in-depth view of the ESP markets and issues. For organisations considering ESP third parties, the research team provides assistance in deciding when, why and what areas to outsource. The team also illustrates the challenges that IS professionals face while selecting and managing these external resources. Also included is a Banking Benchmark, Security Assessment, OS BPG, IT Spending analysis and multi-client studies (ASP and Professional services).?
<p />

Through understanding the critical success factors and pitfalls that others have experienced, organisations reduce their risk in selecting ESP partnerships. Clients learn the "ins and outs" of ESP contract negotiation, as well as strategies to manage ESP vendors and increase the chance for success once the deal has been signed.<p /> 
  </td>
