<tr>
<td valign="top" class="contentText">
EXECUTIVE.IT is the strategy magazine of Gartner for top management in medium and large Italian corporations.  Every month the magazine addresses topics relevant to different sectors in the complex world of Information and Communication Technology.<p />

<img src="//img/executive_it.gif" width="69" height="100" alt="EXECUTIVE.IT Magazine Cover Image"  valign="middle" align="left" vspace="5" hspace="5" />

The themes covered involve not only technology but also its impact on corporate economics, and the ways top management can approach and adapt to change (in production, marketing, sales, distribution, organization, finance).<p />

EXECUTIVE.IT is writen for top managers who are called upon every day to make strategic decisions, from investment to new product development, from organizational design to actions aimed at optimizing profits and improving services for clients.<p />
